{"tid":2390001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★返工=?】今日起工作場所若出現至少兩宗確診個案，將納入強檢公告","createTime":"2021-02-01T09:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T10:45:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"93843a03141ecf28e2e3f636d5203f2cb3c851f5","tid":2390001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:20:48.000Z","msg":"張建宗指，因應疫情需要，預期這段時間有機會每日在全港不同地區，將同時進行以早前北角和觀塘規模相若的受限區域行動，目標在最短時間內達致小區清零。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，當局將降低工作場所強制檢測門檻，今日起工作場所若出現至少兩宗確診個案，將納入強檢公告；而密切接觸者追蹤工作也會加強，密切接觸者的同住成員亦會被要求強檢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573466-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573466-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=91cb420f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573466-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f51b525e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573466-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"688a92df96353b88f132d556c5aa6b6fa610e8e3","tid":2390001,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:21:22.000Z","msg":"返工加送 全穴通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc9775c46ec0d8571682bdfead7facdd19c5312","tid":2390001,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"個個學你唔返工<br />\n<br />\n你又何來有老綜?"},{"pid":"cbdc56bb7959008367ac2b1475715dd07a380f9a","tid":2390001,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"688a92df96353b88f132d556c5aa6b6fa610e8e3","tid":2390001,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cited